ji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc9b2f57362f6c8bed35498de7c6d153c20ccc1d","tid":120661,"uid":2372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T02:58:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>衝出來柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 日本都有啦</blockquote><br />\n日本係有人帶，<br />\n但個感覺唔會覺得自己好型咁，<br />\n而韓國人帶，俾我個印象好似樓主張相咁，<br />\n覺得黑口罩係潮流，覺得好型<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n韓狗好柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cafe5ba6d02750636c4c2c8f30c75c02d4053998","tid":120661,"uid":24345,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T03:04:05.000Z","msg":"On9,日本人不嬲都係戴白色冇款果種普通口罩，唔係依種整色整水冇事冇幹以為好撚型韓狗口罩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n韓狗最鐘意拉日本人落水，正契弟"},{"pid":"fd777b3f03cf96d14b71b2d4afb3f66a40e58def","tid":120661,"uid":2372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T03:16:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>On9,日本人不嬲都係戴白色冇款果種普通口罩，唔係依種整色整水冇事冇幹以為好撚型韓狗口罩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n韓狗最鐘意拉日本人落水，正契弟</blockquote><br />\n韓狗除左泡菜有咩係原創<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}